    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/709b0c6b4cb3b615bf0803d510089d2f.poster.avif?t=1728569135\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/709b0c6b4cb3b615bf0803d510089d2f.webm?t=1728569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/709b0c6b4cb3b615bf0803d510089d2f.mp4?t=1728569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>支持2-8人联机，《The Matriarch》 是一款致命的捉迷藏类派对游戏，每个人都是欺诈者。 融合了社交推理和捉迷藏元素，让所有参与其中的玩家彼此猜疑！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/aac7af7d3bf7bc9717e0ad348f6892a2.avif?t=1728569135\" width=620 height=124 /></span><br>机器人被设计成纯粹的工作者，从挤牛奶到削土豆，他们绝不会质疑老嬷嬷的命令！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/ba14cc008cde8678c8e2f595e95116a5.avif?t=1728569135\" width=620 height=124 /></span><br><strong>“罪人的目标：躲开老嬷嬷，找到出口</strong><br>罪人的外观和机器人一模一样，但是由真正的玩家控制。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>老嬷嬷在场的时候，模仿机器人的行为，以免引起怀疑。<br></li><li>等待合适的机会进入地窖。<br></li><li>挖出一条通道，逃脱修道院。<br></li><li>祈祷夜幕降临之时，老嬷嬷没有怀疑你。 </li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/b130e4c391d1811b24c048a446070f79.avif?t=1728569135\" width=620 height=124 /></span><br><strong>“老嬷嬷目标：识别并献祭所有由玩家控制的罪人。 </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在修道院里面巡逻并观察修女<br></li><li>留意那些有可疑行为的人...<br></li><li>...或者剑走偏锋，杀他个回马枪，抓住并献祭那些罪人</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 随意定制您的游戏：探索不同的地图、体验不同回合时间、随机老嬷嬷等等！<br></li><li> 解锁新的祭祀装置：巨型十字架、断头台、火刑架、铁处女……选择权尽在你手！<br></li><li> 在公共房间里游玩并结识新玩家，或者打开自己的私人房间并与一群朋友一起玩。<br></li><li> 享受免费更新带来更多地图和自定义选项！</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.poster.avif?t=1728569135\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.webm?t=1728569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.mp4?t=1728569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
